Students from Zeta Beta Tau at both the University of Florida and Emory University have been accused of disrespecting disabled veterans during the Warrior Beach Retreat in Panama City on April 17 . 
  They allegedly spat on them and threw beer off the balcony and urinated on the American flag . 
  Three members of the Universityof Florida chapter have been expelled . 
  Both university chapters have suspended all activities . 
  The event is designed to give veterans a break during spring break . 
 